content: Frustrated! The app looks beautiful, so I thought I must be missing something. I actually paid for the Pro version assuming I'd get the "full app" bc the free version is so bare-boned - but there IS NO difference btwn pro and free! All you get are 2 pages for 'offline' & 'online', both nearly identical. 4-5 categories with only a few songs in each. No settings wheel, no menu options, no instructions, no contact info. PAID VERSION DOES NOT HAVE MORE SONGS, CATEGORIES, OPTIONS, INFO - Nothing!
replyContent: We are sorry to hear you are unsatisfied with our app. As we have said in the app description and screenshots; the app has no ads, has more categories and songs. You can find the Learn, Think, Create categories inside the Online section and use the app without the ads. Our contact info is contact@klikklakstudio.com
